Body:
I just wanted to send out a quick reminder about our Philanthropy event
tomorrow night at St. Lukes at 7:00 in toom R25.  Julie and I went shopping
yesterday and purchased all of the treats for inside the care packages.  We
are making 150 carepackages for KIPP kids (about 3 each), so it should take
about an hour.  We will also include inspirational notes inside each package
to personalize the packages and make them fun.  If you have any quote books
or the like - please bring them so that we can include sweet quotes and
thoughts for these kids so far from home.  It should be a fun time!
Remember:

Wednesday, Feb 20
St. Lukes (Westheimer and Edloe)
7:00 p.m. in R25

Thanks!
Ashley and Julie

ps - if you have already let me know that you can not attend, I've got you
down.  If you haven't let me know, please send me a note.

